<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Profesyonel Site</title>

<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72, #2a5298);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
}

header {
    padding: 50px;
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.card {
    background: white;
    color: black;
    margin: 20px auto;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    width: 80%;
    max-width: 400px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

button {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: #2a5298;
    color: white;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

button:hover {
    background: #1e3c72;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<header>
🚀 Benim Web Sitem
</header>

<div class="card">
    <h2>Hakkımda</h2>
    <p>Bu site GitHub ile yapılmıştır.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2>İletişim</h2>
    <p>Bana ulaşmak için tıkla</p>
    <button onclick="mesaj()">Mesaj Gönder</button>
</div>

<script>
function mesaj() {
    alert("Bana ulaştın 😎");
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
